# --- Region updates: pinned event IDs (optional) ---
# The authoritative source of truth for /get_region_updates is the event ID, not
# the event name or creation order. Pin the checkin / piscinego / module event
# IDs per region here. Format: REGION_<NAME>_{CHECKIN,PISCINE,MODULE}_EVENT_ID.
# <NAME> is the campus name (case-insensitive). Any metric left unset falls back
# to the region's default path-based lookup, so leaving all of these blank keeps
# the previous behavior unchanged. A pinned event is verified (exists, belongs to
# the region, not ended) before its stats are trusted.
# Example:
# REGION_ASTANAHUB_CHECKIN_EVENT_ID=12345
# REGION_ASTANAHUB_PISCINE_EVENT_ID=12346
# REGION_ASTANAHUB_MODULE_EVENT_ID=12347